race.description: Road To Magic Millions Book Now Plate (C3)
race.comment: Group 2 placegetter ZOUNA (12) wasn't too far away in much sterner company at Newcastle last time out and will be cherry-ripe for this now fourth run back from a break. Gets the services of Maloney in the irons and can return to the winners' circle. POCKETMONEY (14) has hit a purple patch with two wins and a second from her past three outings and maps ideally for this from gate two. Big chance once again. CENTENNIAL PARK (8) placed around this circuit last time out and looks ready for the step-up to the mile journey now. Include in calculations. LITTLE JEANIE (13) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be slept on.
